subject: Availability Check for UYCL Sessions for Cananda
body:
Hi Rebecca and Juri,
 
We are getting closer to confirming dates for Cananda’s two Understanding Your Cultural Lens sessions. Can you check if these dates and times would work on your end? The Canada team would then select 1 date from round 1 and one date from round 2.
 
Round 1 options:
Tuesday, May 6, 2025 – 10 am – 12 pm ET
Tuesday, May 13, 2025 – 2 pm – 4 pm ET
 
 
Round 2 options:
Tuesday, May 20, 2025 – 2 pm – 4 pm ET
Tuesday, May 27, 2025
 
– 10 am – 12 pm ET
 
Best,
Evan
 
 
Evan Tarshish
DE&I Talent Management Principal Specialist
Enterprise Talent Management
